''Bold textOkokomaiko bụ mpaghara dị n'obodo Ojo, nke dị na Steeti Lagos, ndịda ọdịda anyanwụ Naịjirịa, n'akụkụ Lagos- Badagry ExpresswayGọmentị Lagos Steeti, n'okpuru nduzi nke onye bụbu gọvanọ Akinwunmi Ambode gbatịkwuru mkpa ụzọ a dị na mpaghara West Africa ma nwee atụmatụ ịgbasawanye Lagos-Badagry Expressway ka ọ bụrụ ụzọ awara awiri

Ihe owuwu a malitere site na Eric Moore ruo Okokomaiko. Ambode, n'oge ọ bụ gọvanọ, nabatara onye ọ bụla na-etinye ego nke dị njikere iso gọmentị steeti na-arụkọ ọrụ n'iwu ụzọ mile-2 na Badagry, nke gụnyere mpaghara Okokomaiko

O kwuru na n'oge a, ọrụ amalitelarị site na Eric More ruo Okokomaiko mana anyị dị njikere iso onye ọ bụla na-etinye ego na-achọ ịmalite iwu nkebi nke abụọ nke bụ ụzọ iri site na Okokomaico ruo Seme Border.
